        <div class="hero-sky">
            <div class="hero-birds-img"></div>
            <div class="hero-sky-edge"></div>
            <div class="hero-float-card">
                <div class="hfc-icon">🏆</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="hfc-t">Achievement unlocked!</div>
                    <div class="hfc-s">Sign Language Starter ⭐</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-content-inner">
                <div class="hero-eyebrow">
                    <div class="hero-dot"></div>
                    Inclusive Education Platform
                </div>
                <h1>Learning has<br /><em>no barriers</em><br />here.</h1>
                <p>BridgeUp connects people with disabilities, parents, teachers, and coaches to world-class courses, therapy sessions, sign language tools, and a caring community.</p>
                <div class="hero-btns">
                    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.location='signup.html'">Get started free →</button>
